Package: constRuct
Type: Package
Title: A Framework for Building Stateful ETL Pipelines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Matthew", "Eklund",
      email = "meklund@arrowheadgrp.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: An object-oriented framework for building standardized and
    stateful Extract, Transform, Load (ETL) pipelines. Use R6 classes
    to encapsulate run-specific parameters, data, and logs, promoting
    clean, modular, and reproducible workflows.
